        <mxCell id="vQscuov0rRj8pPbwZavg-35" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=20;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#99CCFF);fontColor=light-dark(#FFF2CC,#1D293B);" value="&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1i073i8&quot; data-start=&quot;50&quot; data-end=&quot;74&quot;&gt;🔥 What this enables&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;76&quot; data-end=&quot;235&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kv9t4f&quot; data-start=&quot;76&quot; data-end=&quot;128&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;78&quot; data-end=&quot;93&quot;&gt;AI Copilots&lt;/strong&gt; → grounded, consistent reasoning&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ae2cks&quot; data-start=&quot;129&quot; data-end=&quot;177&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;131&quot; data-end=&quot;144&quot;&gt;ML Models&lt;/strong&gt; → stronger inputs, less tuning&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1aqmmla&quot; data-start=&quot;178&quot; data-end=&quot;235&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;180&quot; data-end=&quot;198&quot;&gt;Business decision making&lt;/strong&gt;→ fewer dashboards, faster answers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;Across domains, the Signal Discovery Engine does the same thing —&lt;br&gt;it separates what matters from what doesn’t, and turns data into decision-ready signal.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
